Class CompactPrinter

  • java.lang.Object

    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ChunkCompactPrinter

    public class CompactPrinter
extends CodePrinter
implements CssCompilerPass
    A compact-printer for CssTree instances. TODO(oana): Change this pass to stop visiting when definitions are encountered. The same goes for its test.
    Author:
    oana@google.com (Oana Florescu), fbenz@google.com (Florian Benz)
